36
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:39,290
Not a single call. And she's refusing every visit.

37
00:03:39,890 --> 00:03:41,430
Why is she being like this? Seriously.

38
00:03:42,230 --> 00:03:43,330
Hold on.

39
